<div class="container text-white">
    
    <div class="row mt-3">
        <div class="col-12 text-muted">
            <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                            <button class="btn btn-link" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                1.What's this all about?
                            </button>
                        </h5>
                    </div>

                    <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            This is a website made for people to pick a movie to watch or see other people opinions. Everybody can add a review for any movie that is listed. Registration is not mandatory.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                2.How can I register?
                            </button>
                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            If you wish to register , click the "Register" button located on the right part of the screen (or under navigation menu if you use phone).
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                3.How to add a review?
                            </button>
                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            It's very simple. Just find the movie you want to talk about and click the "Add" button below it.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header" id="headingFour">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                                4. I want to delete my account. How?
                            </button>
                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseFour" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            Sorry to hear that. You can't delete your own account by yourself. In order for your account to be deleted write us a mail about your wish and your username. We would appreciate if you write about your reason too.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header" id="headingFive">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                                5. I want to write a review for a movie that I can't find here. What to do?
                            </button>
                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseFive" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            Unfortunately, at this moment you can't add movies by yourself. If you want us to include your movie , please send us a short mail with the title :)
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header" id="headingSix">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseSix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                                6. How to report a user for writing an insulting review?
                            </button>
                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseSix" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSix" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            Send us a short mail about it , including details about the user's name. 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


        </div> 
    </div>
   
</div>
